gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

He will cut down imperishable, the one who knows the bond of his own slave; 
Thus speaking, he has been spoken to by God himself in person.

Here is the translation:

When they tied the tree, then those who gathered there did dance; 
When those of Vastin's village have come, then Shyam has become invisible.

Here is the translation:

The news of the foreign land has spread, you will be told in detail; 
In Saraswati's village, whoever is born, he is called Rama Ji by that name.

Here is the translation:

He showed Rama Patel his face, took her palm as new; 
I say I am taking refuge in you, you keep my news secure.

Here is the translation:

He will stay here for four days, doing darshan with the husband and wife; 
If you know divine limbs, do not stop the song of the heart.
